updateRewardRate.t.sol
├── when the caller is not the owner
│   └── it should revert
└── when the caller is the owner
    ├── when the new reward rate is the same as the old rate
    │   └── it should revert
    └── when the new reward rate is different from the old rate
        ├── when there are no stakers
        │   ├── it should update the reward rate
        │   └── it should emit a RewardRateUpdated event
        └── when there are existing stakers
            ├── it should update the reward rate
            ├── it should emit a RewardRateUpdated event
            ├── it should not affect the rewards already earned by existing stakers
            ├── it should correctly calculate new rewards based on the new rate
            └── when a user stakes after the rate change
                └── it should calculate rewards correctly using the new rate
